 (optional; falls back to 
``OPENAI_API_KEY``
)
Example for LM Studio:
```nu
$env.NU_AGENT_CHAT_URL = \"http://127.0.0.1:1234/v1/chat/completions\"
$env.NU_AGENT_MODEL = \"qwen2.5-coder-7b-instruct\"

```
