``propose-edit``
 -> 
``apply-edit``
 for inspectable edits.
For multi-step requests, the model must emit every requested tool call in order.
For edit preview requests, 
``propose-edit``
 should be used so the preview is surfaced.
Rust is allowed only as 
``nu_plugin``
 extensions exposed back as Nushell tools.
